2005-05-30 14:50  karl

	* trunk/icecast/doc/icecast2_config_file.html,
	  trunk/icecast/src/cfgfile.c, trunk/icecast/src/cfgfile.h,
	  trunk/icecast/src/connection.c, trunk/icecast/src/format_mp3.c,
