	  YP server outage.

2004-05-05 05:05  msmith

	* trunk/icecast/src/auth.c: Use remove() then rename() only on
	  win32 - where it's required. Don't use it on unix systems, which
	  don't need it, and where doing _only_ rename() preserves
	  atomicity.

